text: Cawdor is a village of Wollondilly Shire, in the state of New South Wales, Australia. Part of the locality of Cawdor lies within Camden Council. ==Population== According to the 2016 census, there were 434 residents in Cawdor. 79.0% of people were born in Australia and 88.8% of people spoke only English at home. The most common responses for religion in Cawdor were Catholic 35.2% and Anglican 31.0%. ==References== ==External links== * [CC-By- SA] Category:Towns in New South Wales Category:Towns in the Macarthur (New South Wales) Category:Wollondilly Shire Category:Camden Council (New South Wales)
